 data rate and PU throughput, average PU queueing delay, and average PU\nenergy savings.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 Jun 2014 17:40:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 8 Jul 2014 21:25:45 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 26 Oct 2017 14:39:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-27"}
