fferential kinematics\" is consistent with the scenario of \"differential wind\nrecycling\" proposed by Oppenheimer et al. We discuss the implications for\ngalaxy evolution, the stellar to halo mass function, and the mass metallicity\nrelationship of galaxies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 Jun 2014 20:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 16 Jul 2014 23:19:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-19"}
